## Stan differences function

```
functions {
  real[] logisticgrowth(real t,
                  real[] y,
                  real[] theta,
                  real[] x_r,
                  int[] x_i
                  ) {
    real dydt[x_i[1]];
    for (i in 1:x_i[1]){
      dydt[i] = theta[1] * y[i] * (1-y[i]/theta[2]);
    }
    return dydt;
  }
}
```
## Model with ODE 

```
model {
  real y_hat[T,n_wells];

  y_hat = integrate_ode_rk45(logisticgrowth, y0, t0, ts, theta, x_r, x_i);
  for (t in 1:T) {
    for (i in 1:n_wells) {
      z[t,i] ~ normal(y_hat[t,i], sigma);
    }
  }
  theta ~ cauchy(0,2.5);
  sigma ~ normal(0,0.01);
}
```

